      "content": "Okay, that helps. To really make this argument bulletproof for the judges, I need to tackle the economic aspect too. How can I argue that redlining and these restricted zones actually protected the \"economic health\" and property values of these neighborhoods? I want to frame it as a way for these communities to secure their investments and ensure that the character of the neighborhood wasn't diluted by external factors. Can you give me some specific rationales for how segregation served as a tool for economic protection and stability?",
